ome":19055000.0,"total_cash":39247000.0,"total_cash_per_share":6.205,"total_debt":91255000.0,"debt_to_equity":106.944,"enterprise_value":134619360.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":3.223,"enterprise_to_revenue":0.155,"earnings_growth":-0.244,"shares_outstanding":6325525.0,"float_shares":2078314.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.77385,"held_pct_institutions":0.15703,"beta":0.105,"fifty_two_week_high":13.06,"fifty_two_week_low":11.29,"fifty_day_average":12.75,"two_hundred_day_avg":12.5175,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":14.0,"all_time_low":4.0,"long_business_summary":"Rajvi Logitrade Limited provides transportation and logistics services. It offers port operation services comprising of cargo handling, stevedoring, rake and barge handling, bagging, and warehousing. It also offers transportation services consisting of break bulk cargo, steel, container, project cargo, liquid, material handling, and bulk cargo services. In addition, the company provides custom solutions including import/export, container, exim advising, air cargo, and bonded warehousing solutions. Further, it offers vessel agency, chartering, and survey services; freight forwarding services, as well as provides port related information, customized solutions, and route mapping solutions. Additionally, the company provides various infrastructure services for trucks, trailers, tippers, dumpers, bulkers, pay loaders, excavators, hydraulic hoppers, and mobile cranes. The company was formerly known as Suryakrupa Finance Limited and changed its name to Rajvi Logitrade Limited in May 2023. Rajvi Logitrade Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is based in Gandhidham, India."}}